#: .\Bag.json
msgid "xeas bag"
msgid_plural "xeas bags"
msgstr[0] "xeas袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'xeas bag'}
#: .\Bag.json
msgid "Small lace bag. But large inside!"
msgstr "小型蕾絲袋。但內部空間很大！"

#: .\Boot.json
msgid "pair of xeas boot"
msgid_plural "pairs of xeas boots"
msgstr[0] "xeas靴子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of xeas boot', 'str_pl': 'pairs of xeas
#. boots'}
#: .\Boot.json
msgid "A pair of experimental mix multilayer boots."
msgstr "一雙實驗性混合多層靴子。"

#: .\Gloves.json
msgid "pair of xeas gloves"
msgid_plural "pairs of xeas gloves"
msgstr[0] "xeas手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of xeas gloves', 'str_pl': 'pairs of xeas
#. gloves'}
#: .\Gloves.json
msgid "A pair of xeas experimental mix multilayer gloves."
msgstr "一雙xeas實驗性混合多層手套。"

#: .\Helmet.json
msgid "xeas helmet"
msgid_plural "xeas helmets"
msgstr[0] "xeas頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'xeas helmet'}
#: .\Helmet.json
msgid "A experimental mix multilayer helmet."
msgstr "一項實驗性混合多層頭盔。"

#: .\Mask.json
msgid "xeas mask"
msgid_plural "xeas masks"
msgstr[0] "xeas面罩"

#. ~ Description for xeas mask
#: .\Mask.json
msgid ""
"A experimental, mix multilayer reinforced gas mask. Provides excellent "
"protection from smoke, teargas, and claws. It must be prepared before use."
msgstr "一項實驗性、混合多層加固防毒面具。提供出色的煙霧、催淚瓦斯和爪擊防護。使用前必須準備。"

#: .\Suit.json
msgid "xeas suit"
msgid_plural "xeas suits"
msgstr[0] "xeas套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'xeas suit'}
#: .\Suit.json
msgid ""
"A lightweight, experimental mix multilayer armor made from. Protects from "
"the elements as well as from harm."
msgstr "一套輕量級、實驗性混合多層裝甲，由...製成。既能抵禦環境因素，也能防護傷害。"

#: .\Weapon.json
msgid "xeas knife"
msgid_plural "xeas knives"
msgstr[0] "xeas刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'xeas knife', 'str_pl': 'xeas knives'}
#: .\Weapon.json
msgid ""
"Ultra hi-tech, ultra light experimental knife. Does never get damaged when "
"used as melee weapon."
msgstr "超高科技、超輕量實驗性刀具。用作近戰武器時永不損壞。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "XEAS"
msgstr "XEAS"

#. ~ Description for XEAS
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds new Xeno-Adapted Stuff. Close to hi-tech content. Includes an armor set"
" (slightly better protection than survival armor, less encumbrance), a new "
"knife (better butchering, impression damage) and a vortex bag (120 L, tiny "
"size, no encumbrance). Craft recipes are in vanilla lab journal. High price "
"in terms of money. Late game content!"
msgstr ""
"新增異形適應裝備。接近高科技內容。包括一套裝甲（防護略優於生存裝甲，負重更輕）、一把新刀（更好的屠宰效果，印象傷害）和一個渦流袋（120升容量，極小尺寸，無負重）。製作配方在原版實驗室日誌中。價格高昂。屬於後期遊戲內容！"
